<pb n="0217a" id="I01.0080.0217a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0217a00"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><head type="no">No. 80</head>
<lb ed="C I" n="0217a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>郭顯邕等造一切經記</title></jhead></juan>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0217a01"/><p id="pI01p0217a0101">大唯那
<lb ed="C I" n="0217a02"/>大唯那
<lb ed="C I" n="0217a03"/>大唯那
<lb ed="C I" n="0217a04"/>大唯那</p>
</div2>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b01"/><p id="pI01p0217b0101">夫真宗沖玄。法理難尋。空湛幽<note n="0217001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31035;＝廓【史】</note><app n="0217001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">廓</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31035;</rdg></app>。遠而莫□。自非神智通感。安能曉<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">監</unclear>往
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b02"/>述。慧化津流。非文無以傳於萬古。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">契</unclear>藏之徒。必藉聲教以&CB30397;寤。上第名儒。
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b03"/>亦因言說以<note n="0217002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30304;＝詮【史】</note><app n="0217002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">詮</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30304;</rdg></app>厥義。其有王子。名曰悉達。奉花定光。託陰摩耶。棄彼萬<note n="0217003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31036;＝邦【史】</note><app n="0217003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邦</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31036;</rdg></app>。
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b04"/>不以為珍。盜踰宮闕。軒駕道樹。是以法鼓一擊。則塵沙玉潤。等慈宣暢。隨
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b05"/>□□受。三車之教既周。便尒西謝。輟響靈山。埋光兩樹。斷句韜章。長<note n="0217004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02793;＝彌【史】</note><app n="0217004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02793;</rdg></app>息
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b06"/>照。於是寶船頃壞。法摧□而莫舉。凝神虛寂。飛聲東夏。夢感漢庭。弘興<note n="0217005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31037;＝再【史】</note><app n="0217005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">再</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31037;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b07"/>序。金容雖隱。慧音永盛。風<note n="0217006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB12017;＝軌【史】</note><app n="0217006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">軌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB12017;</rdg></app>慧日。迄今不絕。然此大邑主練行。沙門悲教
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b08"/>二禪師。識度清高。解佩緇門。少投道服。志業&CB07099;為。<note n="0217007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30602;＝整【史】</note><app n="0217007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">整</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30602;</rdg></app>三千而不減。攝六賊
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b09"/>於四禪。秉榮自護。愛惜浮囊。處泥不汙。粲若明珠。復能勸率迷俗。以<note n="0217008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31038;＝示【史】</note><app n="0217008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">示</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31038;</rdg></app>未
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b10"/>悟。次有大經主中丘縣人郭顯邕。可謂樹靈根於九泉。孤條鬱嶷如獨穎。
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b11"/>出自太原。因封關左。上祖郭溫。青冀二州刺史。邕其後也。斯人雖形居塵
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b12"/>境。心栖方外。知炎宅非久之資。睹危城同于并葛。遂共禪師等。契信內融。
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b13"/>崇茲勝福。道素競湊。五百餘人皆是一<app source="0217003" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邦</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31036;</rdg></app>豪<note n="0217009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">桀＝傑【史】</note><app n="0217009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">傑</lem><rdg wit="【原】">桀</rdg></app>。邑里頂最。給孤之徒。脫纓
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b14"/>之侶。建此高節。同<note n="0217010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30896;＝規【史】</note><app n="0217010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">規</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30896;</rdg></app>妙果。於是競捨己財。頃寶弗□。敬造一切經卷。過三
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b15"/>千部□十二。磬竭盡章。不漏巧遺建。祈蠰佉之早遇。泣娑羅之難追。願度
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b16"/>生死流。俱時昇彼岸。功就悠駕。刊銘金石。徽音遐代。千載不易。　頌曰
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b17"/>靈覺闡朗。慧<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">日</unclear>獨曉。眉如初月。含暉皎皎。敷揚四諦。悟果億兆。一坐說法。
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b18"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">&CB03637;</unclear>逕十<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">介</unclear>。人天蒙賴。得道不少。<note n="0217011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00450;＝雙【史】</note><app n="0217011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">雙</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00450;</rdg></app>林變白。現<note n="0217012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31040;＝瑞【史】</note><app n="0217012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">瑞</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31040;</rdg></app>光表。大眾琩F。<note n="0217013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31041;＝憂【史】</note><app n="0217013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">憂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31041;</rdg></app>心悄悄。
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b19"/>澄神空寂。金容<note n="0217014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31039;＝皎【史】</note><app n="0217014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">皎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31039;</rdg></app><app source="0217014" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">皎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31039;</rdg></app>。埋光綴照。哀哉長了。<note place="inline">其一</note>積行累德。道備成功。半偈碎
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b20"/>身。天帝改<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">容</unclear>。位超十住。人中之龍。馳軀西域。一去不東。瓊山崩頹。遺教許
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b21"/>宗。聖言不墜。千稔傳通。<note place="inline">其二</note>新經巨嶽。寶聚巍巍。造化始有。世帝奇希。往<note n="0217015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30136;＝昔【史】</note><app n="0217015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">昔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30136;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b22"/>舍城。今日何期。諸天讚嘆。散華霏霏。魔王奉獻。尼乾歸依。化感寰外。上及
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b23"/>紫微。上矚斯福。見性不疑。<note place="inline">其三</note>神州沃壤。誕生漢賢。存心聖教。重法輕珍。邑
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b24"/>人五百。助德靈仙。雲奔力<note n="0217016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB15137;＝競【史】</note><app n="0217016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">競</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB15137;</rdg></app>。剋就不年。芳延宇宙。振響六天。闡提逢遇。宿
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b25"/>殖有緣。羅王登道。地獄生蓮。含形獲慶。拔苦忘纏。刊石雕文。永劫不遷。<note place="inline">其四</note>
<lb ed="C I" n="0217b26"/>　　　　　　　　大齊天統元年歲次大梁九月庚辰朔六日乙酉</p>
